Hello, we tried upgrading  through deploying the MSI file through our MDM, but received an unknown fatal error. We tried enabling debug logging and running again, but no new logs seem to have been generated.
Subject: Netwrix Support Ticket #424690 - Upgrade Froze Many Systems and Failed on Roughly Half

TextBody:
Hi,

To see install logs please append this to the misiexec command: /l*v <path_to_>EPPClientSetup.log and make sure to replace the <path_to_> with the local patch on the computer, usually, other customers point to the Desktop folder to make sure they have write access.
After that send me the file and I can check it out. Of course, you can open it and somewhere at the bottom of the file, you should see the reason it fails.
Also, try manually installing the agent on one computer to see if there are other issues besides the MDM deployment.
Please let me know your timezone and availability if you need assistance, and I will set it up.

Thank you,
Eduard Nut
Technical Support Engineer
